Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.60,0:08:50.68,DCMain,UKISHIMA,0,0,0,,{\be1.8}سامحوني
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:54.83,DCMain,TOMOKO,0,0,0,,{\be1.8}أنا آسفة
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:01.27,DCMain,MOVER,0,0,0,,{\be1.8}المعذرة
